title: JF Musial (Founder of /DRIVE, Director)
description: This week J.F. Musial (Johnny Samsonite) and Duncan Ende join us to talk about Nino getting a ticket, E3, drinking games, the McLaren P1, Porsche 918 and a return to the drunken melee that was signature of early episodes.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
